{
  "video_id": "MIA_1xQc7x8",
  "title": "The inside story of the Paris climate agreement | Christiana Figueres",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15416.0,
      "text": "I have one more reason for optimism:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15440.0,
      "end_time": 16896.0,
      "text": "climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16920.0,
      "end_time": 19680.0,
      "text": "Maybe you don&#39;t believe it, but here is the fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20400.0,
      "end_time": 23799.0,
      "text": "On December 12, 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 27216.0,
      "text": "in Paris, under the United Nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27240.0,
      "end_time": 31695.0,
      "text": "195 governments got together"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31720.0,
      "end_time": 33879.0,
      "text": "and unanimously --"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 37816.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;ve worked with governments, you know how difficult that is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37840.0,
      "end_time": 40560.0,
      "text": "unanimously decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40800.0,
      "end_time": 44896.0,
      "text": "to intentionally change the course of the global economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44920.0,
      "end_time": 47736.0,
      "text": "in order to protect the most vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47760.0,
      "end_time": 50416.0,
      "text": "and improve the life of all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50440.0,
      "end_time": 52855.0,
      "text": "Now, that is a remarkable achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52880.0,
      "end_time": 55960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55120.0,
      "end_time": 57256.0,
      "text": "But it is even more remarkable"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57280.0,
      "end_time": 61256.0,
      "text": "if you consider where we had been just a few years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61280.0,
      "end_time": 63936.0,
      "text": "2009, Copenhagen."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63960.0,
      "end_time": 65600.0,
      "text": "Who remembers Copenhagen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66160.0,
      "end_time": 71735.0,
      "text": "Well, after years of working toward a climate agreement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71760.0,
      "end_time": 74920.0,
      "text": "the same governments convened in Copenhagen"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76800.0,
      "end_time": 78390.0,
      "text": "and failed miserably."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78640.0,
      "end_time": 81160.0,
      "text": "Why did it fail miserably?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81400.0,
      "end_time": 82616.0,
      "text": "For many different reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82640.0,
      "end_time": 86176.0,
      "text": "but primarily because of the deeply entrenched divide"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86200.0,
      "end_time": 88920.0,
      "text": "between the global North and the global South."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90720.0,
      "end_time": 94616.0,
      "text": "So now, six months after this failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94640.0,
      "end_time": 97976.0,
      "text": "I was called in to assume the responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98000.0,
      "end_time": 100560.0,
      "text": "of the global climate change negotiations."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100800.0,
      "end_time": 104456.0,
      "text": "You can imagine, the perfect moment to start this new job."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104480.0,
      "end_time": 108176.0,
      "text": "The global mood on climate change was in the trash can."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 110656.0,
      "text": "No one believed"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110680.0,
      "end_time": 113640.0,
      "text": "that a global agreement could ever be possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114160.0,
      "end_time": 116200.0,
      "text": "In fact, neither did I."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117160.0,
      "end_time": 121976.0,
      "text": "If you promise not to tell anyone outside of this wonderful TED audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122000.0,
      "end_time": 124960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to divulge a secret"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 124120.0,
      "end_time": 128480.0,
      "text": "that has been gratefully buried by history."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129600.0,
      "end_time": 132296.0,
      "text": "On my first press conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132320.0,
      "end_time": 135696.0,
      "text": "a journalist asked, \"Um, Ms. Figueres,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135720.0,
      "end_time": 140960.0,
      "text": "do you think that a global agreement is ever going to be possible?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140120.0,
      "end_time": 144456.0,
      "text": "And without engaging brain, I heard me utter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144480.0,
      "end_time": 146790.0,
      "text": "\"Not in my lifetime.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147240.0,
      "end_time": 150776.0,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine the faces of my press team"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150800.0,
      "end_time": 154496.0,
      "text": "who were horrified at this crazy Costa Rican woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154520.0,
      "end_time": 155920.0,
      "text": "who was their new boss."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156720.0,
      "end_time": 159336.0,
      "text": "And I was horrified, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159360.0,
      "end_time": 162616.0,
      "text": "Now, I wasn&#39;t horrified at me, because I&#39;m kind of used to myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162640.0,
      "end_time": 164815.0,
      "text": "I was actually horrified"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164840.0,
      "end_time": 168536.0,
      "text": "at the consequences of what I had just said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168560.0,
      "end_time": 170736.0,
      "text": "at the consequences for the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170760.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "in which all our children are going to have to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176240.0,
      "end_time": 179560.0,
      "text": "It was frankly a horrible moment for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179800.0,
      "end_time": 181176.0,
      "text": "and I thought, well, no, hang on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181200.0,
      "end_time": 182816.0,
      "text": "hang on."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182840.0,
      "end_time": 186656.0,
      "text": "Impossible is not a fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186680.0,
      "end_time": 188120.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an attitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 188800.0,
      "end_time": 191176.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only an attitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191200.0,
      "end_time": 196136.0,
      "text": "And I decided right then and there that I was going to change my attitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 196160.0,
      "end_time": 200799.0,
      "text": "and I was going to help the world change its attitude on climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201760.0,
      "end_time": 204736.0,
      "text": "So I don&#39;t know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204760.0,
      "end_time": 206736.0,
      "text": "No, just this? Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206760.0,
      "end_time": 207959.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210120.0,
      "end_time": 211656.0,
      "text": "what you would do"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211680.0,
      "end_time": 217120.0,
      "text": "if you were told your job is to save the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217960.0,
      "end_time": 219760.0,
      "text": "Put that on the job description."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221400.0,
      "end_time": 223696.0,
      "text": "And you have full responsibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223720.0,
      "end_time": 226856.0,
      "text": "but you have absolutely no authority,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226880.0,
      "end_time": 230720.0,
      "text": "because governments are sovereign in every decision that they take."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 232560.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "Well, I would really love to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236400.0,
      "end_time": 238296.0,
      "text": "what you would do on the first Monday morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238320.0,
      "end_time": 240736.0,
      "text": "but here&#39;s what I did: I panicked."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 240760.0,
      "end_time": 242416.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 242440.0,
      "end_time": 244936.0,
      "text": "And then I panicked again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 244960.0,
      "end_time": 249000.0,
      "text": "because I realized I have no idea how we&#39;re going to solve this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 249800.0,
      "end_time": 253856.0,
      "text": "And then I realized I have no idea how we&#39;re going to solve this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253880.0,
      "end_time": 256815.0,
      "text": "but I do know one thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256839.0,
      "end_time": 261815.0,
      "text": "we have got to change the tone of this conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 261839.0,
      "end_time": 264936.0,
      "text": "Because there is no way you can deliver victory"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 264960.0,
      "end_time": 266159.0,
      "text": "without optimism."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267400.0,
      "end_time": 268616.0,
      "text": "And here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 268640.0,
      "end_time": 273176.0,
      "text": "I use optimism as a very simple word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 273200.0,
      "end_time": 275976.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s understand it in its broader sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 276000.0,
      "end_time": 278896.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s understand it as courage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 278920.0,
      "end_time": 282896.0,
      "text": "hope, trust, solidarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282920.0,
      "end_time": 287816.0,
      "text": "the fundamental belief that we humans can come together"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287840.0,
      "end_time": 291119.0,
      "text": "and can help each other to better the fate of mankind."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 291800.0,
      "end_time": 294416.0,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine that I thought that without that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294440.0,
      "end_time": 297896.0,
      "text": "there was no way we were going to get out of the paralysis of Copenhagen."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 297920.0,
      "end_time": 299736.0,
      "text": "And for six years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299760.0,
      "end_time": 305616.0,
      "text": "I have stubbornly, relentlessly injected optimism into the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 305640.0,
      "end_time": 308496.0,
      "text": "no matter what the questions from the press --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 308520.0,
      "end_time": 310695.0,
      "text": "and I have gotten better at those --"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 310720.0,
      "end_time": 313896.0,
      "text": "and no matter what the evidence to the contrary."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 313920.0,
      "end_time": 319400.0,
      "text": "And believe you me, there has been a lot of contrary evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 321360.0,
      "end_time": 325640.0,
      "text": "But relentless optimism into the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 326880.0,
      "end_time": 328856.0,
      "text": "And pretty soon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 328880.0,
      "end_time": 334216.0,
      "text": "we began to see changes happening in many areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 334240.0,
      "end_time": 337496.0,
      "text": "precipitated by thousands of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 337520.0,
      "end_time": 340135.0,
      "text": "including many of you here today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 341360.0,
      "text": "and I thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342400.0,
      "end_time": 347136.0,
      "text": "And this TED community will not be surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 349776.0,
      "text": "if I tell you the first area"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 349800.0,
      "end_time": 352936.0,
      "text": "in which we saw remarkable change"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 352960.0,
      "end_time": 354159.0,
      "text": "was ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 355320.0,
      "end_time": 356520.0,
      "text": "technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 357600.0,
      "end_time": 360216.0,
      "text": "We began to see that clean technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 360240.0,
      "end_time": 362696.0,
      "text": "in particular renewable energy technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 362720.0,
      "end_time": 365336.0,
      "text": "began to drop price and increase in capacity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365360.0,
      "end_time": 368416.0,
      "text": "to the point where today we are already building"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 368440.0,
      "end_time": 370176.0,
      "text": "concentrated solar power plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 370200.0,
      "end_time": 374656.0,
      "text": "that have the capacity to power entire cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 374680.0,
      "end_time": 378816.0,
      "text": "to say nothing of the fact of what we are doing on mobility"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 378840.0,
      "end_time": 380719.0,
      "text": "and intelligent buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 381400.0,
      "end_time": 384215.0,
      "text": "And with this shift in technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 384240.0,
      "end_time": 387416.0,
      "text": "we were able to begin to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387440.0,
      "end_time": 391000.0,
      "text": "that there was a shift in the economic equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 391720.0,
      "end_time": 393816.0,
      "text": "because we were able to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393840.0,
      "end_time": 396936.0,
      "text": "that yes, there are huge costs to climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 396960.0,
      "end_time": 399496.0,
      "text": "and yes, there are compounded risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 399520.0,
      "end_time": 402176.0,
      "text": "But there also are economic advantages"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 402200.0,
      "end_time": 403896.0,
      "text": "and intrinsic benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 403920.0,
      "end_time": 406856.0,
      "text": "because the dissemination of the clean technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 406880.0,
      "end_time": 408880.0,
      "text": "is going to bring us cleaner air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410640.0,
      "end_time": 412150.0,
      "text": "better health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 412400.0,
      "end_time": 414576.0,
      "text": "better transportation, more livable cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 414600.0,
      "end_time": 416136.0,
      "text": "more energy security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 416160.0,
      "end_time": 419616.0,
      "text": "more energy access to the developing world."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 419640.0,
      "end_time": 422680.0,
      "text": "In sum, a better world than what we have now."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 423840.0,
      "end_time": 425520.0,
      "text": "And with that understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 426840.0,
      "end_time": 430335.0,
      "text": "you should have witnessed, in fact, part of you were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 430360.0,
      "end_time": 434696.0,
      "text": "the spread of ingenuity and excitement"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 434720.0,
      "end_time": 438736.0,
      "text": "that went through, first through nonnational governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 438760.0,
      "end_time": 442896.0,
      "text": "the private sector, captains of industry, insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 442920.0,
      "end_time": 447216.0,
      "text": "investors, city leaders, faith communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 447240.0,
      "end_time": 452576.0,
      "text": "because they all began to understand, this actually can be in their interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 452600.0,
      "end_time": 456120.0,
      "text": "This can actually improve their bottom line."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 457840.0,
      "end_time": 463599.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t just the usual suspects."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 464760.0,
      "end_time": 470560.0,
      "text": "I have to tell you I had the CEO of a major, major oil and gas company"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 470800.0,
      "end_time": 472416.0,
      "text": "come to me at the beginning of last year"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 472440.0,
      "end_time": 473640.0,
      "text": "and say --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 474520.0,
      "end_time": 476280.0,
      "text": "privately, of course --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 477280.0,
      "end_time": 481135.0,
      "text": "he did not know how he was going to change his company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 481160.0,
      "end_time": 483336.0,
      "text": "but he is going to change it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 483360.0,
      "end_time": 486400.0,
      "text": "because he&#39;s interested in long-term viability."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 486840.0,
      "end_time": 492150.0,
      "text": "Well, now we have a shift in the economic equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 492400.0,
      "end_time": 496376.0,
      "text": "and with that, with broader support from everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 496400.0,
      "end_time": 502775.0,
      "text": "it did not take very long before we saw that national governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 502800.0,
      "end_time": 507656.0,
      "text": "woke up to the fact that this is in their national interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 507680.0,
      "end_time": 511816.0,
      "text": "And when we asked countries to begin to identify"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 511840.0,
      "end_time": 515736.0,
      "text": "how they could contribute to global efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 515760.0,
      "end_time": 518960.0,
      "text": "but based on their national interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 518120.0,
      "end_time": 522376.0,
      "text": "189 countries out of 195,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 522400.0,
      "end_time": 527736.0,
      "text": "189 countries sent their comprehensive climate change plans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 527760.0,
      "end_time": 529895.0,
      "text": "based on their national interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 529919.0,
      "end_time": 531816.0,
      "text": "concurrent with their priorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 531840.0,
      "end_time": 535320.0,
      "text": "consistent with their national sustainable development plans."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 536680.0,
      "end_time": 537880.0,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 538800.0,
      "end_time": 543976.0,
      "text": "once you protect the core interests of nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 544000.0,
      "end_time": 547656.0,
      "text": "then you can understand that nations were ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 547680.0,
      "end_time": 551295.0,
      "text": "to begin to converge onto a common path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 551320.0,
      "end_time": 554576.0,
      "text": "onto a common direction of travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 554600.0,
      "end_time": 557736.0,
      "text": "that is going to take us probably several decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557760.0,
      "end_time": 560256.0,
      "text": "but over those several decades is going to take us"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 560280.0,
      "end_time": 561736.0,
      "text": "into the new economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 561760.0,
      "end_time": 565336.0,
      "text": "into a decarbonized, highly resilient economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 565360.0,
      "end_time": 568736.0,
      "text": "And the national contributions that are currently on the table"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 568760.0,
      "end_time": 571560.0,
      "text": "on behalf of national governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 571800.0,
      "end_time": 575216.0,
      "text": "are insufficient to get us to a stabilized climate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 575240.0,
      "end_time": 577296.0,
      "text": "but they are only the first step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 577320.0,
      "end_time": 579336.0,
      "text": "and they will improve over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 579360.0,
      "end_time": 583776.0,
      "text": "And the measurement, reporting and verification of all of those efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 583800.0,
      "end_time": 585455.0,
      "text": "is legally binding."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 585480.0,
      "end_time": 589216.0,
      "text": "And the checkpoints that we&#39;re going to have every five years"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 589240.0,
      "end_time": 593736.0,
      "text": "to assess collective progress towards our goal are legally binding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 593760.0,
      "end_time": 598656.0,
      "text": "and the path itself toward a decarbonized and more resilient economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 598680.0,
      "end_time": 599880.0,
      "text": "is legally binding."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 602496.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the more important part:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 602520.0,
      "end_time": 603936.0,
      "text": "What did we have before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 603960.0,
      "end_time": 607160.0,
      "text": "A very small handful of countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 607400.0,
      "end_time": 610280.0,
      "text": "who had undertaken very reduced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 611320.0,
      "end_time": 614376.0,
      "text": "short-term emission reduction commitments"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 614400.0,
      "end_time": 617576.0,
      "text": "that were completely insufficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 617600.0,
      "end_time": 621160.0,
      "text": "and furthermore, largely perceived as a burden."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 621400.0,
      "end_time": 622456.0,
      "text": "Now what do we have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 622480.0,
      "end_time": 628560.0,
      "text": "Now we have all countries of the world contributing with different intensities"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 630376.0,
      "text": "from different approaches in different sectors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 630400.0,
      "end_time": 633880.0,
      "text": "but all of them contributing to a common goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 635400.0,
      "end_time": 637496.0,
      "text": "and along a path"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 637520.0,
      "end_time": 639560.0,
      "text": "with environmental integrity."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 640400.0,
      "end_time": 644456.0,
      "text": "Well, once you have all of this in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 644480.0,
      "end_time": 646696.0,
      "text": "and you have shifted this understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 646720.0,
      "end_time": 651960.0,
      "text": "then you see that governments were able to go to Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 651120.0,
      "end_time": 653656.0,
      "text": "and adopt the Paris agreement."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 653680.0,
      "end_time": 656319.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 661360.0,
      "end_time": 662560.0,
      "text": "So,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 663280.0,
      "end_time": 664800.0,
      "text": "as I look back"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 668440.0,
      "end_time": 670560.0,
      "text": "over the past six years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 674000.0,
      "end_time": 675480.0,
      "text": "first I remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 676480.0,
      "end_time": 680800.0,
      "text": "the day the Paris agreement was adopted."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 680800.0,
      "end_time": 683376.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you the euphoria in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 683400.0,
      "end_time": 686776.0,
      "text": "5,000 people jumping out of their seats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 686800.0,
      "end_time": 690455.0,
      "text": "crying, clapping, screaming, yelling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 690480.0,
      "end_time": 695776.0,
      "text": "torn between euphoria and still disbelief at what they had just seen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 695800.0,
      "end_time": 697640.0,
      "text": "because so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 698440.0,
      "end_time": 703120.0,
      "text": "had worked for years towards this, and this was finally their reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 704480.0,
      "end_time": 708720.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t just those who had participated directly."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 709600.0,
      "end_time": 712376.0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, I was with a colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 712400.0,
      "end_time": 714216.0,
      "text": "who was trying to decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 714240.0,
      "end_time": 719440.0,
      "text": "on a Tahitian pearl that he wanted to give to his wonderful wife Natasha."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 721160.0,
      "end_time": 725199.0,
      "text": "And once he had finally decided what he was going to buy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 726760.0,
      "end_time": 727976.0,
      "text": "the jeweler said to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 728000.0,
      "end_time": 730816.0,
      "text": "\"You know, you&#39;re very lucky that you&#39;re buying this now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 730840.0,
      "end_time": 735520.0,
      "text": "because these pearls could go extinct very soon because of climate change.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 736240.0,
      "end_time": 739776.0,
      "text": "\"But,\" the jeweler said, \"have you heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 739800.0,
      "end_time": 742575.0,
      "text": "the governments have just come to a decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 742600.0,
      "end_time": 745840.0,
      "text": "and Tahiti could have a chance.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 746800.0,
      "end_time": 750160.0,
      "text": "Well, what a fantastic confirmation"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 750400.0,
      "end_time": 754550.0,
      "text": "that perhaps, perhaps here is hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 754800.0,
      "end_time": 756800.0,
      "text": "here is a possible chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 757640.0,
      "end_time": 762295.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the first one to recognize that we have a lot of work still to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 762320.0,
      "end_time": 765656.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve only just started our work on climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 765680.0,
      "end_time": 769376.0,
      "text": "And in fact, we need to make sure that we redouble our efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 769400.0,
      "end_time": 773199.0,
      "text": "over the next five years that are the urgent five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 774640.0,
      "end_time": 777496.0,
      "text": "But I do believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 777520.0,
      "end_time": 780456.0,
      "text": "that we have come over the past six years"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 780480.0,
      "end_time": 781680.0,
      "text": "from the impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 782440.0,
      "end_time": 784536.0,
      "text": "to the now unstoppable."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 784560.0,
      "end_time": 789616.0,
      "text": "And how did we do that? By injecting transformational optimism"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 789640.0,
      "end_time": 793960.0,
      "text": "that allowed us to go from confrontation to collaboration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 793120.0,
      "end_time": 796416.0,
      "text": "that allowed us to understand that national and local interests"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 796440.0,
      "end_time": 799816.0,
      "text": "are not necessarily at odds with global needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 799840.0,
      "end_time": 802555.0,
      "text": "and that if we understand that, we can bring them together"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 802579.0,
      "end_time": 804815.0,
      "text": "and we can merge them harmoniously."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 804840.0,
      "end_time": 808576.0,
      "text": "And as I look forward to other global issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 808600.0,
      "end_time": 812456.0,
      "text": "that will require our attention this century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 812480.0,
      "end_time": 816960.0,
      "text": "food security, water security, home security, forced migration --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 819800.0,
      "end_time": 821496.0,
      "text": "I see that we certainly do not know"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 821520.0,
      "end_time": 825550.0,
      "text": "how we are going to solve those problems yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 825800.0,
      "end_time": 829776.0,
      "text": "But we can take a page out of what we have done on climate change"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 829800.0,
      "end_time": 831550.0,
      "text": "and we can understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 831800.0,
      "end_time": 837376.0,
      "text": "that we have got to reinterpret the zero-sum mentality."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 837400.0,
      "end_time": 842376.0,
      "text": "Because we were trained to believe that there always are winners and losers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 842400.0,
      "end_time": 844400.0,
      "text": "and that your loss is my gain."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 844640.0,
      "end_time": 846736.0,
      "text": "Well, now that we&#39;re in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 846760.0,
      "end_time": 849696.0,
      "text": "in which we have reached planetary boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 849720.0,
      "end_time": 852376.0,
      "text": "and that we are not just so interconnected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 852400.0,
      "end_time": 855816.0,
      "text": "but increasingly interdependent on each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 855840.0,
      "end_time": 858000.0,
      "text": "your loss is no longer my gain."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 858760.0,
      "end_time": 861240.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re either all losers"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 862160.0,
      "end_time": 864896.0,
      "text": "or we all can be winners."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 864920.0,
      "end_time": 867216.0,
      "text": "But we are going to have to decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 867240.0,
      "end_time": 870400.0,
      "text": "between zero and sum."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 871400.0,
      "end_time": 875896.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to have to decide between zero benefit for all"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 875920.0,
      "end_time": 879896.0,
      "text": "or living life as the sum of all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 879920.0,
      "end_time": 882256.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve done it once. We can do it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 882280.0,
      "end_time": 883496.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 883520.0,
      "end_time": 888948.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}